{"tid":1836290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎擴散 德法領導人打電話給習近平","createTime":"2020-01-23T06:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T07:33:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"470b9c2e7cae0e5ef732abef0ff279b7f3d279d0","tid":1836290,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"湖北省武漢肺炎疫情已擴散至其他國家，德國總理梅克爾(Angela Merkel)和法國總統馬克宏(Emmanuel Macron)22日分別致電中方表達支持和協助之意，中國國家主席習近平則指願與世界衛生組織在內的國際社會加強合作應對疫情。<br />\n<br />\n據中國外交部官網，習近平在22日分別應約與梅克爾和馬克宏通電話，兩國領導人對武漢肺炎疫情表達了關切。<br />\n<br />\n梅克爾表示，德方讚賞中方及時應對新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情，保持公開透明，並積極開展國際合作，德方願向中方提供支持和協助；馬克宏則說，法方支持中方積極應對新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情，願和中方加強衛生合作。<br />\n<br />\n對於兩國領導人的表態，習近平表示感謝，強調中方願與世界衛生組織(WHO)在內的國際社會加強合作，有效應對疫情，維護全球衛生安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2049146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2049146&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=20002728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2049146</a>"},{"pid":"7bf834333049bbea651ae11465755ccb5765c35b","tid":1836290,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/9a/-%E8%B3%AD%E4%BF%A0-God.of.Gamblers.II.1991.BluRay.720p.x264.AC3_2018%E5%B9%B43%E6%9C%8817%E6%97%A5_%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%887.00.46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F9a%2F-%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E4%25BF%25A0-God.of.Gamblers.II.1991.BluRay.720p.x264.AC3_2018%25E5%25B9%25B43%25E6%259C%258817%25E6%2597%25A5_%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25887.00.46.png&h=d2880fcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb28c68163daffa66e1cefc26aa2782741925e6e","tid":1836290,"uid":115910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"習：又唔係我中，你打俾我把撚咩"},{"pid":"c340f010362e1f17bdbc835534330edc00943a53","tid":183629